long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension redirects the search to GPTGo.AI, the free ChatGPT hybrid search engine.

GPTGO, formerly known as GooGPT, is a perfect combination of Google's search technology and ChatGPT's breakthrough artificial intelligence. Inspired by these two leading technology resources, GPTGO has rapidly developed into a reliable and efficient search tool.

Features of GPTGO
GPTGO combines the best features of Google's search technology and ChatGPT, along with many other useful features.

Search results combined with free ChatGPT
In addition to search results from Google, GPTGO.AI also provides creative answers from ChatGPT for free, helping users to have a more diverse view of the information they are searching for.

Unlimited free use of ChatGPT
GPTGO.AI allows users to experience ChatGPT for free without worrying about usage restrictions.

Super-fast speed
GPTGO.AI ensures extremely fast search and response speed from ChatGPT, helping users save time.

Easy copying and downloading of content
GPTGO.AI provides the convenient feature of copying and downloading ChatGPT content, supporting users in storing and reusing information.
